---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import bil from "../assets/images/bil.webp";
import bilde1 from "../assets/images/mikroplast1.webp";
import bilde2 from "../assets/images/mikroplast2.webp";
import bilde3 from "../assets/images/mikroplast3.webp";
import bilde4 from "../assets/images/mikroplast4.webp";
---

<section
  class="lg:mt-[65rem] md:mt-[50rem] mt-7 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto"
  id="start"
>
  <h2>Hvad er plastikforurening?</h2>
  <p>
    Når plastikmaterialer ophober sig i naturen, gør det skade på både miljøet,
    dyrelivet og menneskers sundhed!
  </p>
  <p>
    Hvert år udledes der <span class="text-[#FF1054] text-[32px] leading-none"
      >8-10 mio. ton
    </span> plastik til havet
  </p>
  <p>
    Det svarer til <span class="text-[#FF1054] text-[32px] leading-none">1 lastbil </span> med
    plastik, der tømmes <span class="text-[#FF1054] text-[32px] leading-none"
      >hvert minut!
    </span>
  </p>
</section>

<section class="mb-12">
  <div class="flex justify-end">
    <Image src={bil} alt="lastebil" class="w-2/4" />
  </div>
</section>
<section class="max-w-2xl mx-12 md:mx-auto mb-44">
  <h3>Du spiser plastik hver dag</h3>
  <article class="md:grid grid-cols-3 mt-6 md:gap-20 pt-6">
    <div class="col-start-1 col-span-2">
      <Image src={bilde1} alt="flaske bliver til mikroplastik" />
    </div>
    <div class="col-start-3 col-span-1 flex self-center justify-self-center">
      <h4 class="md:text-xl text-sm mt-4">
        Sollys og bølger nedbryder plastik til mikroplastik
      </h4>
    </div>
  </article>
  <article class="md:grid grid-cols-3 mt-6 md:gap-20 pt-6">
    <div class="order-2 col-span-2">
      <Image src={bilde2} alt="mikroplastik og gift" />
    </div>
    <div class="order-1 col-span-1 flex self-center justify-self-center">
      <h4 class="md:text-xl text-sm mt-4">
        Mikroplastik suger miljøgifte og farlige kemikalier til sig
      </h4>
    </div>
  </article>
  <article class="md:grid grid-cols-3 mt-6 md:gap-20 pt-6">
    <div class="col-start-1 col-span-2">
      <Image src={bilde3} alt="fisk spiser plastik" />
    </div>
    <div class="col-start-3 col-span-1 flex self-center justify-self-center">
      <h4 class="md:text-xl text-sm mt-4">
        Havdyrene indtager de giftige stoffer, når de spiser mikroplastikken
      </h4>
    </div>
  </article>
  <article class="md:grid grid-cols-3 mt-6 md:gap-20 pt-6">
    <div class="order-2 col-span-2">
      <Image src={bilde4} alt="fisk på tallerken" />
    </div>
    <div class="order-1 col-span-1 flex self-center justify-self-center">
      <h4 class="md:text-xl text-sm mt-4">
        Til sidst indtager vi mennesker de giftige stoffer, når vi spiser
        fiskene
      </h4>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>
